description.name: Hotel Mazurka
description.description: Come to our family run hotel with clean and cosy rooms and excellent local food. Historical centre of Dragolm is within walking distance. Upon interest, we can arrange guided tours in Dragolm.

roomTypes.name: Single room - economy
roomTypes.description: A small room with a single bed. The bathroom is located in the hallway and is shared with other rooms.

roomTypes.name: Single room - standard
roomTypes.description: Standard single-bed room with a private bathroom.

roomTypes.name: Family room
roomTypes.description: A larger room with one double bed and two separate beds and a private bathroom.
